{"tid":609667,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"入唻諗下呢條問題","createTime":"2018-03-29T08:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T10:26:04.000Z","uid":138752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"175205deaaf09e1741c68989b9043292d9f15455","tid":609667,"uid":138752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:26:30.000Z","msg":"參賽者會看見三扇關閉了的門，其中一扇的後面有一輛汽車或者是獎品，選中後面有車的那扇門就可以贏得該汽車或獎品，而另外兩扇門後面則各藏有一隻山羊或者是後面沒有任何東西。當參賽者選定了一扇門，但未去開啟它的時候，知道門後情形的節目主持人會開啟剩下兩扇門的其中一扇，露出其中一隻山羊。主持人其後會問參賽者要不要換另一扇仍然關上的門。<br />\n(Monty hall problem)<br />\n<br />\n問題是：換另一扇門會否增加參賽者贏得汽車的機會率？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ca793e92d7b93c3975adaa4840812dc553c1ec","tid":609667,"uid":178742,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"唔換,無影響"},{"pid":"2c6a1c203f96dfa74acd6d8fde4ab36a4cdbf8b8","tid":609667,"uid":138752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45ca793e92d7b93c3975adaa4840812dc553c1ec","tid":609667,"uid":178742,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"唔換,無影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efb5b9d90cc5dcaaf02a26edc073b6329147fce","tid":609667,"uid":138752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"過兩頁開估，心急想知答案嘅可以google下"},{"pid":"7d5623542f5c39df125412a0797d3cc3ead142c5","tid":609667,"uid":64336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:37:52.000Z","msg":"換機率變高<br />\n利申 睇伯賴"},{"pid":"67e4ec57efb899186b5055e51387e8e409ef38f3","tid":609667,"uid":33972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45ca793e92d7b93c3975adaa4840812dc553c1ec","tid":609667,"uid":178742,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"唔換,無影響"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:40:51.000Z","msg":"咁你諗下如果唔係三度門, 係三十度門呢?<br